        <section class="container">
                    <h1 class="u-entryTitle">Pick the sweetest, ripest fruit with this science-based guide</h1>
          <p class="Article-excerpt">
  Stop and smell the tomatoes. No seriously, it helps.
</p>

<p class="Article-author">
                    <span class="Article-byLine">
          By
        </span>
                              <a href="https://www.popsci.com/authors/sara-chodosh/"
             rel="author"
             class="fn author-link">
            Sara Chodosh
          </a>
                
              |
    <span class="Article-dateTime">
    <time datetime="2023-08-18T18:20:04-04:00">
    Updated Aug 18, 2023 6:20 PM EDT
    </time>
  </span>
</p>
<ul class="Article-categories">
      <li>
      <a href="https://www.popsci.com/category/environment/">
        Environment
      </a>
    </li>
